heading: Witchwater Dungeon Guide
content: Witchwater contains both Snakes and Spiders, two dangerous monster types that can , and explode on death. It also has a linear, straightforward layout. Despite its difficulty, it is decent for farming, but is not currently a possible . Slither is an annoying Boss with multiple abilities that are difficult to avoid.
